description:
Part 2: 
In this video, I cover sealing the headlights and where I routed the LightingTrendz wires, positioning of all the components in the engine bay, and wiring to switched power, so the DRLs only get power when the vehicle is turned on or in ACC mode.

BUY ME A COFFEE/BEER:
https://www.buymeacoffee.com/squarewheels

Email for enquiries:
square@square-built.com

Hit me on IG if you have any questions: https://www.instagram.com/squarewheelsauto
YOU CAN DO THIS!  

0:00 - Intro & THANKS!!
0:59 - View Part 1 First
1:27 - Coming soon - Sequentials, Demon Eyes, BlueGhozt
2:19 - How I ran LightingTrendz wires out of the headlight
3:19 - Reinstalling headlights & Running Wires
4:11 - Testing for switched 12V power
5:04 - Where I tapped for switched 12V power
7:24 - Rough wiring & placement diagram
7:49 - Securing & Waterproofing
9:30 - Quick LightingTrendz LEDHue App Demo
